<h4>Greetings!</h4>

<p>
  <strong><%= link_to @resource.invited_by.name, user_url(@resource) %></strong> has invited you to join Photographer.io - a new photo sharing community for photography enthusiasts. Because they've invited you, you both get an additional <%= ISO[:defaults][:upload_referral_bonus] %> uploads per month as our way of saying thank you :)
</p>

<p>
  To accept your invite and get started, click the following link:
</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Accept invitation', accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @resource.invitation_token), class: "button" %></p>

